Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.39,0:00:25.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以哦  小鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.55,0:00:33.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.22,0:02:17.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那接下來就給“這裡”上刑吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.59,0:02:20.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手  那裡絕對不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.49,0:02:24.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就～不～住～手～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.07,0:02:27.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我投降  投降
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.41,0:02:29.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這也太用力了吧！？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.78,0:02:30.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.70,0:02:34.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你自己嫌麻煩不涂防曬霜嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.69,0:02:37.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你再輕一點嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.86,0:02:39.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那接下來涂這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.14,0:02:44.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.72,0:02:48.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  接下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.61,0:02:50.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛茜亞？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.52,0:02:53.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.50,0:02:54.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.54,0:02:57.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢喜歡純一嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.58,0:03:01.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  不要突然問我這種事情啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.55,0:03:04.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然  要說喜不喜歡的話那當然是喜歡了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.42,0:03:08.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過  那個  沒有什麼別的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.85,0:03:10.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.23,0:03:14.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.43,0:03:15.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.04,0:03:17.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.77,0:03:28.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢喜歡純一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.59,0:03:32.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥也喜歡純一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.65,0:03:37.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是  小鳥卻不說出真實想法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.01,0:03:41.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為朝倉君他現在很幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:44.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢也很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.33,0:03:48.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水越  美春還有大家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.93,0:03:51.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在這樣是最幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.18,0:03:54.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以小鳥才不說出口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.45,0:03:57.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這樣大家才都幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.36,0:04:04.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣是不對的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.21,0:04:09.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:12.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為必須大家每個人都幸福才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.53,0:04:15.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有她一個人不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.89,0:04:20.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣…這樣…肯定是不對的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.63,0:04:36.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  是愛茜亞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.51,0:04:38.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好  有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.79,0:04:42.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.20,0:04:48.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了  稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.98,0:04:50.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海邊拍的照片已經衝好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:52.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫我交給朝倉君好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.63,0:04:54.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.10,0:04:58.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥  你到我家來好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:05:00.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  去朝倉君家？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.42,0:05:04.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,純一他…  正傷腦筋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.64,0:05:10.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實習要在外邊住宿？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.22,0:05:14.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  所以現在音夢不在家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.52,0:05:17.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後純一他說不喜歡我做的飯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.07,0:05:21.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天天吃便利店的盒飯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.22,0:05:23.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以想讓小鳥你來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.98,0:05:28.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,買東西的話我隨時可以幫忙…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.65,0:05:30.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓小鳥來做飯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.13,0:05:32.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像以前那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:35.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.52,0:05:41.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也好久沒來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.15,0:05:43.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.31,0:05:47.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我平時不常來這家店的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.61,0:05:52.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥  我要拿嘍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:54.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  朝倉君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.28,0:05:55.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一…  二！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.64,0:06:05.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也留著…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.24,0:06:07.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這兩年來的回憶…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.48,0:06:11.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行  這昨天剛買過吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.21,0:06:16.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也有…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.44,0:06:18.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,炒麵色拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.13,0:06:20.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,試試看吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.82,0:06:22.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那好吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.12,0:06:23.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肯定很好吃的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.80,0:06:29.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…就一天的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.22,0:06:30.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:31.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了愛茜亞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.93,0:06:35.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一日限定後勤部隊  就再活動一回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.01,0:06:38.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥…  嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.24,0:06:57.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也有…回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.63,0:06:59.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.48,0:07:02.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.61,0:07:04.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.44,0:07:07.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們走吧  朝倉君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.32,0:07:23.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.38,0:07:26.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:32.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像沒人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:39.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  是歌丸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.67,0:07:44.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥  音夢和純一現在都出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.55,0:07:47.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢…不是去實習了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:49.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.51,0:07:50.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之先進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.59,0:07:57.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…朝倉君回來的晚嗎  愛茜亞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:00.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:03.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了  反正只做個色拉而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.14,0:08:16.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥  看起來很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.90,0:08:21.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？  大概是因為很久沒這樣做了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:24.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  接下來該切黃瓜…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.59,0:08:26.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？  砧板呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.08,0:08:29.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  放到這邊來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.17,0:08:30.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.10,0:08:32.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.65,0:08:37.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  菜刀在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.57,0:08:39.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.26,0:08:41.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.55,0:08:42.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都換地方了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.06,0:08:47.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  音夢說這樣用起來比較方便
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.73,0:08:50.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:57.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,純一一定會很高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.68,0:09:00.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為他前一陣子還說想吃小鳥做的菜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.23,0:09:03.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.83,0:09:12.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是炒麵色拉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.06,0:09:15.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對  其實很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.94,0:09:18.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉君說他已經吃上癮了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.53,0:09:20.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是先冰一下比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.24,0:09:30.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,致哥哥和愛茜亞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.59,0:09:32.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天會稍微晚點回來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.65,0:09:34.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們晚飯吃這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.71,0:09:35.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.78,0:09:39.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.53,0:09:45.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:49.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:52.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.11,0:09:56.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以後不要再這樣做了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.14,0:10:01.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.72,0:10:05.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.89,0:10:07.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥剛才還很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.16,0:10:11.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來純一家  給純一做飯  顯得很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:15.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥明明喜歡純一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.68,0:10:17.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不對純一說呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.67,0:10:22.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為現在這樣才是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.86,0:10:23.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.82,0:10:25.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.88,0:10:31.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥是大騙子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.68,0:10:48.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.09,0:10:51.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來來來  拿走拿走！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.79,0:10:54.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們這的頭獎  巨大巧克力香蕉！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:56.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對要抽中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.36,0:11:00.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賭上我全日本巧克力香蕉愛好者協會首任會長的名義
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.44,0:11:02.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也一定要抽中它
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.11,0:11:08.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（不中）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.66,0:11:09.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.28,0:11:12.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.77,0:11:14.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再挑戰一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.66,0:11:16.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美春…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.20,0:11:18.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說好了一起逛的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.62,0:11:20.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像得花不少時間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.43,0:11:26.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐去向不明  白河又說有事無論如何都脫不開身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.33,0:11:28.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多點協調精神好不好啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.16,0:11:30.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥她也？  真少見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.12,0:11:36.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法  我們繼續向前吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.82,0:11:38.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:39.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:40.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.70,0:11:45.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想為大家做點好吃的火鍋…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.47,0:11:48.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是蘋果糖火鍋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.97,0:11:52.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又甜又酸的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.71,0:11:53.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.13,0:11:55.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.47,0:11:56.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐你……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:11:58.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這邊看來也挺費時間的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.59,0:11:59.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.88,0:12:00.13,DefaultS,,0000,0000,0000,,不要隨便做起生意好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.57,0:12:10.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.36,0:12:14.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊啊  饒了我吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.07,0:12:21.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個主題不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.83,0:12:28.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.80,0:12:32.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐畫的真好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.25,0:12:34.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吶吶  也畫畫我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.01,0:12:39.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請稍等…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.71,0:12:43.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊～  人手不夠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.06,0:12:44.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.01,0:12:46.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.25,0:12:49.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看你挺忙的  忍不住就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.12,0:12:52.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.68,0:12:55.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知什麼時候變成兩人獨處了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.78,0:12:58.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛茜亞也不知道跑到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.37,0:12:59.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦  朝倉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.22,0:13:01.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歷老師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.56,0:13:02.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來的正好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.03,0:13:07.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉打擾你們相處了  能幫個忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.82,0:13:11.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居委會的醫療站人手不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.35,0:13:13.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:15.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再有不到一個小時  就有人來幫忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.81,0:13:17.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這之前能拜託你頂一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.44,0:13:22.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧  我不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.79,0:13:24.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.07,0:13:26.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.30,0:13:28.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待會請你吃雜煎菜餅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.64,0:13:29.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,記得是特大的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.06,0:13:30.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.31,0:13:31.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.51,0:13:33.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.82,0:13:42.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  結果又剩我一個人了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.50,0:13:54.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥是大騙子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.99,0:13:56.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騙子…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.11,0:14:01.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今年夏天一定得補回這兩年來和朝倉君相處的時間啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:06.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騙子…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.22,0:14:08.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白河小鳥是大騙子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.77,0:14:11.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.32,0:14:14.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉君！？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.19,0:14:20.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了  也不用叫她出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.87,0:14:25.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.72,0:14:31.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼晚了在女孩子家的門口晃來晃去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.24,0:14:32.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很可疑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.95,0:14:35.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.49,0:14:37.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…找小鳥…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:38.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找我？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.52,0:14:40.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對  找你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.48,0:14:43.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  你不是有事出去了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.88,0:14:47.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  已經辦完了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.55,0:14:49.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們去廟會嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.19,0:14:53.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我不知什麼時候變成孤身一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.21,0:14:55.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:14:57.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美春眼裡只有香蕉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.06,0:14:59.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萌前輩當然是弄火鍋了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.01,0:15:04.54,DefaultS,,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲看樣子是要打算創下撈金魚的世界紀錄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.58,0:15:02.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.46,0:15:04.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是說出口的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.64,0:15:07.27,DefaultS,,0000,0000,0000,,阿環在別人的神社幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.00,0:15:08.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.39,0:15:11.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我沒有勉強你去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.36,0:15:13.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且也已經很晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.52,0:15:15.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見  小鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.88,0:15:16.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.03,0:15:22.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  我馬上去換衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.28,0:15:29.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.04,0:15:33.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想再騙自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.24,0:15:40.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我真正的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.30,0:15:44.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我夢想的情景
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:51.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和你一起笑  一起哭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.47,0:16:00.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在你身邊  感受你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.17,0:16:03.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永遠…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.51,0:16:10.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在你身旁  感受你的內心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.00,0:16:14.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永遠…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.68,0:16:22.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.10,0:16:32.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:15.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再往這邊來點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.52,0:17:16.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.35,0:17:21.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,浴衣（一種薄和服）都打濕了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.18,0:17:22.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:30.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.29,0:17:36.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.13,0:17:39.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.67,0:17:44.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.53,0:17:50.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.17,0:17:55.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才在那邊找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.82,0:17:58.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我還沒表示這兩年來的謝意嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.67,0:18:03.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.94,0:18:05.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,純一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.04,0:18:17.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我馬上去換
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.22,0:18:18.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.79,0:18:21.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.41,0:18:28.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就要這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.35,0:18:46.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.26,0:18:50.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼沒有說呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.26,0:18:55.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為那樣最好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.20,0:18:56.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.53,0:19:03.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛茜亞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.18,0:19:06.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.55,0:19:09.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有騙你  真的很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.22,0:19:16.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服的風啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.72,0:20:59.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.95,0:21:01.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.21,0:21:05.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給  海邊拍的照片已經洗好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.00,0:21:06.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就拿來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.35,0:21:08.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.95,0:21:10.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.29,0:21:14.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥  音夢她去實習不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.78,0:21:16.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.63,0:21:20.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉後勤部隊已經停止營業了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.28,0:21:23.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見  愛茜亞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.90,0:21:27.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.61,0:21:29.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是我的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.62,0:21:31.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.40,0:21:34.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.77,0:23:14.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位～  夏天來嘍
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.32,0:23:18.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說到夏天  那還得是火鍋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.43,0:23:22.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在耀眼的陽光照射下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.10,0:23:26.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃一口滾燙滾燙的火鍋最是別有一番風味
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.33,0:23:33.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當中又數放了大量韭菜和紅辣椒的\N「牛雜碎火鍋」最有營養
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.16,0:23:37.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最適合補充體力了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.65,0:23:39.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多吃一點  這個…
